      "content": "The board isn't worried about the \"mess\" of inclusivity, they're worried about the brand damage from being seen as discriminatory. If we move to a new model, it'll be designed specifically to capture all demographics ethically. Why do you think your current \"data-driven\" approach is so much better than a framework designed to actually engage these underserved groups?",
